+Add a !view command

Usage:
!view [nomination(s) | vote(s)]

If in a valid state displays current nominations or voting status (Vote must be open and non secret)

!vote random <1 | 2 | 3> //Vote by a list of acceptable movie IDs
!vote random //Vote fully randomly
!vote random <A | B | C> //Vote by a list of acceptable movie titles
